```class Solution {
    public boolean canConvertString(String s, String t, int k) {
        int diff = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            int sc = s.charAt(i) - 'a';
            int tc = t.charAt(i) - 'a';
            if (sc != tc) {
                diff += Math.abs(sc - tc);
                if (diff > k % 26) return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
}```
